                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list_item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "The concerned manufacturer will necessarily provide information about the remaining stock of the previous financial year to the Deputy Director and Assistant Director of Agriculture (Ext.) office in the district. The grant will not be admissible in the absence of information."
